high_descs: Turn to your left and walk straight, then turn to the sofa to your right
Pick up the left newspaper on the sofa
Turn to your left, then left  again face the foot rest
Place the newspaper on top of the left laptop
anns.task_desc: Put the newspaper on top of the laptop

high_descs: Move across the room to the left side of the largest sofa in the room
Pick up the newspaper that is on top of the sofa on the far left
Carry the newspaper to the ottoman sitting opposite of the sofa
Place the newspaper between the two laptop computers on top of the ottoman
anns.task_desc: Move a newspaper from on top of the sofa to the ottoman

high_descs: Turn around and cross the room to stand in front of the couch with a paper on it.
Pick the paper up from the couch.
Turn around and face the ottoman in front of the couch.
Put the paper on the ottoman.
anns.task_desc: Put a paper on the ottoman.

high_descs: Turn and cross the room to stand between the sofa and ottoman so you're facing the sofa.
Pick up the leftmost newspaper from the sofa.
Carry the newspaper to stand at the end of the ottoman closest to the wall.
Place the newspaper on the left front corner of the ottoman so it's in front of one laptop and to the left of the other laptop.
anns.task_desc: Move a newspaper to the ottoman.

high_descs: Turn around, walk to the couch on your right, and walk to it's leftmost side.
Pick up the newspaper on the left of the couch.
Turn around and face the ottoman.
Place the newspaper on the laptop on the ottoman that is closest to the couch.
anns.task_desc: Place a newspaper on an ottoman.

high_descs: Turn around from facing the door and walk towards the windows on the other side of the room, turn to your right before you reach the furniture with two laptops on it, walk to the couch.
Go to the side of the couch to the left of the laptop behind the white and brown cylindrical pillow.
Pick up of the leftmost newspaper nearest to the keys, turn around towards the furniture holding two laptops.
As you face the left sides of the laptops, put the paper down next to the computer farthest from you and behind the computer closest to you.
anns.task_desc: Move a newspaper from the couch to the furniture directly in front of it.
